1953;;Meet Me at the Fair;;American;;Douglas Sirk;;Dan Dailey, Diana Lynn, Hugh O'Brian;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meet_Me_at_the_Fair;;Zerelda King is assigned to look into possible illegal and unethical activity at an orphanage, which may or may not involve her fiance.<br><br>A boy named Tad flees from the orphanage, meantime, and is given a ride by Doc Tilbee, a man with a traveling medicine show.